 have 1 Woo Theme and 3 WooCommerce Extensions to add to our compatibility list. </p>\n<p>The theme is <a title="Function theme" href="http://www.woothemes.com/products/function/">Function theme</a> and the WooCommerce extensions are <a title="Bulk Stock Management" href="http://www.woothemes.com/products/bulk-stock-management/">Bulk Stock Management</a>, <a title="Extra Product Options" href="http://codecanyon.net/item/woocommerce-extra-product-options/7908619">Extra Product Options</a>, <a title="Table Rate Shipping" href="http://bolderelements.net/plugins/table-rate-shipping-woocommerce/">Table Rate Shipping</a></p>\n<p>If you want to review the entire multilingual ready list of themes and plugins you are welcome to view it here:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a title="Multilingual Ready Themes " href="https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/">Multilingual Ready Themes</a></li>\n<li><a title="Multilingual Ready Plugins " href="https://wpml.org/documentation/plugins-compatibility/">Multilingual Ready Plugins</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Also, if you&#8217;re a theme or a plugin author and you want to make it compatible with WPML, we welcome you and ready to help: You are welcome to contact us at <a href="https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/go-global-program/">go global program page</a>.</p>\n<p>In order to expedite the process we strongly recommend that you test your theme or plugin with our <a title="Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins" href="https://wpml.org/documentation/support/achieving-wpml-compatibility-for-your-themes-and-plugins/">Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins</a>. It easily tests compatibility with WPML and helps you quickly make your theme or plugin <strong>Multilingual Ready</strong>.</p>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center">Function theme</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://www.woothemes.com/products/function/" ><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-340493" src="https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/function1.png" alt="ekho" width="590" height="300" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>A clean, responsive business, blogging and store theme with an advanced featured slider with carousel pagination.</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://www.woothemes.com/products/function/">Purchase Function theme</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center">Bulk Stock Management</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://www.woothemes.com/products/bulk-stock-management/"></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Edit product and variation stock levels in bulk via this handy interface</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://www.woothemes.com/products/bulk-stock-management/" target="_blank">Purchase Bulk Stock Management</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center">Extra Product Options</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://codecanyon.net/item/woocommerce-extra-product-options/7908619"></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Creates extra price fields globally or per product.</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://codecanyon.net/item/woocommerce-extra-product-options/7908619">Purchase Extra Product Options</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center">Table Rate Shipping</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://bolderelements.net/plugins/table-rate-shipping-woocommerce/"></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Return choices of shipping costs each based on a variety of conditions.</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://bolderelements.net/plugins/table-rate-shipping-woocommerce/">Purchase Table Rate Shipping</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=WZXcMo7lO9o:MmgaoJnE03I:D7DqB2